            "text": "highlighting parallels between the pathophysiology of these metabolic abnormalities and the disease course of COVID-19 . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 12,
            "parent": 8,
            "text": "I also discuss how metabolism at the cellular , tissue and organ levels might be harnessed",
